{"tid":2371658,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★點拎？中電向80萬合資格家庭派發總值100元消費券","createTime":"2021-01-19T04:52:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-19T05:06:53.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f3340adfc9d35eb3b69e1d49f50b1a2013f2b95b","tid":2371658,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T04:52:05.000Z","msg":"中電透過中電社區節能基金，撥款超過8000萬元，首次推出為期半年的中電消費券計劃，向近80萬個合資格家庭派發總值100元的消費券，於超過2400間零售店舖及食肆使用。<br />\n<br />\n中電說，本月起將消費券陸續發送至合資格家庭，希望能帶動消費，為各行業注入經濟動力。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1571154-20210119.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1571154-20210119.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=aWm579aYkHvvwdD7ZyOwrOf4PGxNkgPyFAzKtVao6pc%3D&h=e74217f8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1571154-20210119.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=c20e8d8e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1571154-20210119.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"e24602a683e778aade5b92e34e5cb1e5b4bf04c8","tid":2371658,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T04:52:41.000Z","msg":"點叫&ldquo;合資格家庭&rdquo;？<br />\n<br />\n要blue?"},{"pid":"ea4acbff2f40ec2640d64e63e477fa704423c923","tid":2371658,"uid":6435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e24602a683e778aade5b92e34e5cb1e5b4bf04c8","tid":2371658,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T04:52:41.000Z","msg":"點叫&ldquo;合資格家庭&rdquo;？<br />\n<br />\n要blue?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T04:54:00.000Z","msg":"1. 哪些客戶符合資格可獲資助?<br />\n<br />\n此計劃惠及接近80萬個家庭，包括低用電量*住宅客戶、享有長者電費優惠的客戶和10,000個劏房住戶^。<br />\n*低用電量指於2019年全年每期電費賬單(每兩個月一期，即共6張賬單) ，平均用電量不多於500度。<br />\n^劏房住戶須經由參與計劃的中電社區夥伴提名。<br />\n2. 客戶如何得知符合資格並獲取消費券?<br />\n<br />\n由2021年1月1日起，合資格客戶將收到隨2021年第一張電費賬單一併寄出的總值100港元消費券(面值50港元兩張)。選用電子賬單的客戶亦將以郵寄方式收到消費券。<br />\n所有合資格客戶將於2021年2月底或之前收到消費券。<br />\n劏房戶則會透過與中電合作協助劏房戶的社區夥伴派發。"},{"pid":"0a68afb431be9788ee1527e02b3ed282c5c5ccf5","tid":2371658,"uid":117301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T04:54:54.000Z","msg":"岩資格就會電費單連conpon寄比你"},{"pid":"41de4636375123ebc117a99f465b8299312577d4","tid":2371658,"uid":68556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T04:56:21.000Z","msg":"已經收到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"742c0d073c5f61c220f4cf112db0bb17feae27e2","tid":2371658,"uid":121058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T05:06:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZP4UHDo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZP4UHDo.jpg&h=b01649fa&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n玩咩 平均500度先有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}